My Pong game, that runs on node.js

Localhost should be replaced with computer IP so that you could play from other machines.

First two people who connect to the link can play, others watch.

There are 2 ways to controle the paddle:
  1. Arrow keys - up and down
  2. Mobile phone - tilting it up or down
  (By accelerationg mobile on the x-axis, you can add speed to the ball)
